data.name: WARE_ACME_032_1
data.text:
OKAY,JOE--NOW YOU
                TAKE THAT TINGCAN AND
                I'LL TAKE THIS TINGCAN AN YOU GO HIDE IN THE TALL GRASS AN WE
                WILL HAVE OURSELF A SECRIT
                CONVERSASHIN!

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_3
data.text: MAKE SURE YOU CROWCH DOWN REAL GOOD SO AS TO MAKE IT EXTRY SECRIT!

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_5
data.text:
AN LISSEN CLOSE CUZ I YAM ABOUT TO SEND YOU THE
                SECRIT MESSIGE! IS YOU LISSENIN CLOSE?

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_6
data.text:
YES, I YAM LISSENING
                CLOSE TO THE TINGCAN,
                TEX!

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_7
data.text: gsnurt OKAY, CUZ THE MESSIGES ALMOS' REDDY!

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_8
data.text:
OKAY TEX I YAM REDDY
                FOR MY SECRIT TINGCAN
                MESSIGE!

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_9
data.text:
YOU STUPID SON OF A
                BITCH YOU STUPID GOD
                DAMN SON OF A BITCH

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_10
data.text:
WHAT WOULD YER
                MAW HAVE THOUGHT?
                WHAT WOULD YER POOR
                MAW HAVE THOUGHT,
                TEX?!

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_12
data.text:
ALL RIGHT,
                MR.JOHNSON--JOE IS O.K. FOR NOW, BUT IT'LL
                TAKE SOME TIME BEFORE WE KNOW IF
                HIS HEARING WILL EVER RETURN ON
                THAT SIDE

data.name: WARE_ACME_032_13
data.text:
HA HA IT'S OKAY
                TEX, DON' WORRY-- IT DON' HURT TOO
                BAD--I KNOW YOU WAS ONLY HAVING
                A LIL'FUN HAHA--BUT WE'S
                STILL GOOD FRENS, RIGHT? WE'S STILL PALS, AIN'T WE TEX?
